Installation Instructions
*************************

Building the software
=====================

DrQueue uses scons for building (and later on installing)

To build the main DrQueue command line tools and the Gtk+ 
GUI drqman just type:

$ scons

Installing the binaries
=======================

This section needs to be updated. Please refer to the wiki
for details on the subject.

Python
======

The python module uses setuptools. The generic approach for
it whould be:

$ cd python
$ sudo python setup.py install

You'll need root privileges for system-wide installation


